==English==
===Etymology===
Chinese [[關係]], [[关系]] (guānxi<!---xi is neutral tone when used in this sense (connections, who you know) --->), relations.

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/'kuanɕi/}}

===Noun===
'''guanxi'''

# (In the context of Chinese society) [[connection]]s; [[relationship]]s; one's social or business [[network]]
#:''To open a new business in China you need '''''guanxi'''''.''

